<header><section>
<p>Well, we didn't see THAT coming</p>
</section></header><div><section>
<figure><a title="Indie World" href="https://images.nintendolife.com/23a1560abed4b/indie-world.large.jpg"></a><figcaption><em>Image: Nintendo Life / Damien McFerran</em></figcaption></figure><p>For the second week in a row, Nintendo will be holding another showcase for games coming to the Switch and Switch 2.</p>
<p>This time, it's an Indie World, and will be taking place on <strong>7th August at 6am PT / 9am ET / 2pm BST / 3pm CEST</strong>. The showcase will be roughly 15 minutes long and will be show in all of the usual spots.</p>

<p>Folks, we've <em>just</em> had a Partner Showcase â€” which some found disappointing. There might be some rather lovely surprises in store here, though. Let's wait and see!</p>
